snippet.title: Ascendum - Official Release Trailer
snippet.description:
After 4,5 years, Ascendum, my first commercial game, is finally going to be released!
Ascendum on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1504090/Ascendum/

Help 2 twin vessels on their journey through the afterlife! Overcome platforming and mind-bending puzzle challenges, and defeat enemies and bosses while controlling both characters at the same time or working together with another player in local Co-op.

Team Caecus Discord:
https://discord.gg/GtZar6DZr4

Play Ruins of Albion on Steam:
https://store.steampowered.com/app/1719100/Ruins_of_Albion/

Wishlist Virium on Steam:
https://store.steampowered.com/app/1923230/Virium/

Caecus on social media:
Twitter: https://twitter.com/TCaecus
Tumblr: https://teamcaecus.tumblr.com/

Follow the composer Lukian:
Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/lukianze/
Soundcloud: https://soundcloud.com/user-864799849-361065325
